{"tid":2421283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［一邊播毒一邊做大外宣］中共官媒「新華社」於紐約時代廣場落廣告  宣稱中國援助逾80個地區","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T17:25:11.000Z","uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"78f1c305b264421dcdcfd85d4587639cf2c224b2","tid":2421283,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:40:53.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織（WHO）溯源專家組下周將公布在中國武漢的溯源調查初步報告之際，中共官媒新華社於美國紐約時代廣場落廣告做「大外宣」。<span class=\"red\">新華社於廣告表示中國已援助超過80個國家及地區</span>，更表示中國會與全球各國團結對抗武漢肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n中共官媒新華社<span class=\"red\">自2011年起，經營紐約時代廣場的一塊電子廣告板，這塊電子廣告板因此有「中國熒幕」</span>（China Screen）之稱。據悉，<span class=\"red\">該熒幕通常展示中國產品或中國旅行促銷宣傳</span>，但最近卻刊登新廣告。<br />\n<br />\n美國《霍士新聞》（Fox News）報道，新華社刊登的廣告主題為<span class=\"red\">「戰疫，全球一起上」（WE ARE ONE），宣揚中國在抗疫方面取得的成績。廣告指出中國的武漢肺炎患者康復率達48.52% ，遊輪亦通過武肺病毒檢測等。</span><br />\n<br />\n廣告更指中國已經在抗疫方面援助超過80個國家和地區，並加入包括意大利、日本和韓國等國家的照片，同時指出中國<span class=\"red\">「將繼續與國際社會攜手對抗病毒」。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ThYLtnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThYLtnL.jpg&h=5758baae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2885626/</code></pre>"},{"pid":"fa37f6b9d4b9ab1e5d6ad4ff388de53ec9ef4679","tid":2421283,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"報道認為，中國<span class=\"red\">對世衞調查不夠配合，中國在這氣氛下卻拼命宣傳抗疫，「很奇怪」，據稱世衞專家在中國訪查時曾與中國官員有「激烈討論」，世衞發言人賈撒列維克（Tarik Jasarevic）對霍士新聞僅稱：「對話有時候很強烈、有挑戰性」。</span><br />\n<br />\n時代廣場電子廣告屏幕隸屬Sherwood證券旗下的戶外看板公司，霍士新聞向該公司詢問廣告屏幕的出租事宜，暫未獲回應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210224/53IPYYRH4RCQ7KDMTGGJWJV5IY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210224%2F53IPYYRH4RCQ7KDMTGGJWJV5IY%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Ic%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=92adee54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210224%2F53IPYYRH4RCQ7KDMTGGJWJV5IY%2F&h=93b9c57a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210224/53IPYYRH4RCQ7KDMTGGJWJV5IY/</a>"},{"pid":"7f2c4f6c506568c280c0a935fcd2c4ed3b9cf0e5","tid":2421283,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"玩火"},{"pid":"42f97f04072abc1d08345499727cd65ef6f308eb","tid":2421283,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"出殘體版比支那人打飛機"},{"pid":"183f08b349d5b574fc0b04795be8707db079facd","tid":2421283,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"美利堅特別行政區"},{"pid":"ce39a17ff172edf246bf07bafdf74aeec681ad35","tid":2421283,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"專制政權利用民主體制宣傳獨裁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df0c3fcf5bf27ccffb844a5f008022eae35ff3b","tid":2421283,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce39a17ff172edf246bf07bafdf74aeec681ad35","tid":2421283,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"專制政權利用民主體制宣傳獨裁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"呢啲政治宣傳唔可以出現喺民主國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fea6a106c619d24796cab95c2f22195eda7603","tid":2421283,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc9608781dbcc68879879a9a126a64a4fe47bff","tid":2421283,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5df0c3fcf5bf27ccffb844a5f008022eae35ff3b","tid":2421283,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce39a17ff172edf246bf07bafdf74aeec681ad35","tid":2421283